data.description: NEW PRICE!  Welcome to Deer Wood Hollow ~A wonderful Bungalow nestled on a 3.54 acre parcel in the mountain community of Seeley Lake Montana. Built in 1994 this 1,752 Sq Ft. 2 bedroom 1 bath has maintained the original architectural features: Aches, open spaces & natural lightm while the internal workings have been updated. Full remodel of Bathroom,  Soapstone Woodburning Stove warm & cozy. New light fixtures & window treatments throughout. Fresh paint & stain inside and out! It's  Peaceful here.  Beautiful Land, mixed stands of trees, old & new growth, fuel mitigated for the health of the forest. Large fenced garden with raised beds & green house. The stone bridge entry sets the tone of the home. "Warm and welcoming" from the moment you enter the paved driveway.  2 stall carport w/insulated work room. A 10x16 Redwood Shed for ample storage, additional parking. North Boundary Borders 11.78 Acre Horse Property~Privacy! Fire Pit and sledding hill on property.. Fun!   MOVE IN READY!
